  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is served in the La Fontane restaurant offering a selection of Italian and International dishes.</p>
<p>Dinner can be enjoyed in La Bouganville Grill- Pizzeria, which is located by the swimming pool. </p>
<p> </p>
<p>There is also an option to include All Inclusive, which you can call to book. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
